Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:10.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}名も無き罪に　付けられた傷で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:17.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心閉ざし　無理をして笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:23.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}幸せな日々　君はどこかに捨てて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:29.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}詩人のように　孤独　愛してた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:34.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fs20\pos(472,8.8)}い  ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:34.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\pos(640,35)}色彩を奪われた　灰色の街
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:42.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}僕がいるよ　解き放って翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:45.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}抱きしめるから恐れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:48.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}壊れるまで叫ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:54.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}神を殺す言葉さえここにはあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:57.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}2人交わり　ひとつになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}裸足のまま歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:13.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}壁を越えた空の果て　聴こえてくる愛の歌が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:54.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}響徹樂園的歌聲  回蕩在我心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:10.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}無名之罪的枷鎖  讓人痛苦窒息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:17.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}強顏歡笑的背後  是內心築起的孤寂高牆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:23.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}幸福的時光  已被你塵封於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:29.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如同詩人一般  愛上踽踽獨行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:34.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}被剝奪了一切色彩的灰色街道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:42.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}有我在這  你不再是折翼的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:45.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不用害怕  我會將你擁入懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:48.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}撕心裂肺般地吶喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:54.55,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}即便那是弒神之語  也有我與你一起肩負
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:57.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}化為一體的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就這樣赤足前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:13.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}一起譜寫  這跨越一切障礙  震徹雲霄的愛之歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:11.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}羽が舞い散る静寂の場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:16.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}逃げるように消えてく影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:22.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}サヨナラが運命なのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:28.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}喜んで受け入れましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:38.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}読み捨てられた絵本のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:44.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}優しさ達滲んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:49.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}眠りにつくまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:55.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不器用な愛をあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:23:00.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}涙流すこと　笑うことさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:06.03,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}ぎこちない日から　おかしいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:08.83,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}だれかと似ていて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:11.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}うまく生きれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:14.73,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}また会えるのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:19.81,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}その時はすべて伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:23.74,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}キミに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:11.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在漫天飛羽的寂靜之地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:16.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如同逃走般消失的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:22.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}分別如果是命中注定的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:28.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}就請高興地接受它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:38.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}彷彿匆匆過目的圖畫書一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:44.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}滲透著濃濃的溫情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:49.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}直到你入睡為止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:55.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}將我笨拙的愛傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:23:00.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}無論是傷心還是歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:06.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}從遭遇悲痛的那天起  我就變得不再是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:08.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就像某人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:11.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}無法好好地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:14.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}若是還能再相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:19.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}想把心中的一切都
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:23.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}告訴你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,IN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:18:00.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}迷子の子供みたい  うつむいて泣いてたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:11.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}安心できる場所が  ようやく見つかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:23.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}キミが残してくれた  記憶に抱かれて眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:37.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}みんなに伝えて欲しい  あの人を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:42.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}名前呼んでも　指で触れても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:48.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}からかうように　口付けしても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:54.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}照れくさそうな  笑顔はもう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:19:06.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}なくて　どこを見てもいない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:18.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}少しだけ先歩くキミの後ろ追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:24.09,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}次に捕まえた時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:32.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}もう離さない　二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:18:00.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如同迷路的孩子一般  眼淚劃過垂下的兩頰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:11.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}好不容易找到了  能使自己安心的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:23.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如今卻只能沉浸在  對你的回憶中入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:37.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}想要讓大家知道  我深愛著那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:42.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}即便呼喚你的名字  即使用手指輕觸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:48.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}亦或是調皮般地輕輕一吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:54.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}你那害羞般的笑容也已經
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:19:06.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不復存在  消失在了彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:18.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}追尋著你先行一步的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:24.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}下次抓住你時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:32.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}再也不會將手鬆開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TXT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,墜崖第十三天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古森她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古森她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古森同學誤吃了花苗倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來到這裡已經第幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第十三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖地睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊吹同學由於缺乏維生素  意識恍惚的時間增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井同學出現了敗血症的症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廣岡同學已經連反應都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就這樣沉睡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心臟不再跳動的話該有多輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在放棄還言之尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還不是地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界還有活下去的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:18.00,TXTE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(750,200)}『墜崖第十四天』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經餓到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前吃的那點肉  反而激起了更強的食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣才能得救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我弟弟的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見…雄二？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這是我弟弟的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能活著回去  就介紹你認識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會喜歡他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是期待呢  說定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  說定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  失敗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廣岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廣岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這一天傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廣岡同學離開了人世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去挖個墳把她埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們大家都變得奇怪起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心中抱著她死了也是無可奈何的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個多麼卑鄙的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.04,TXTE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(756,210)}『墜崖第十五天』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人活著就會有死去的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這便是這個世界的絕對法則
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天櫻井學姐和古森同學死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻井學姐的死因是敗血症
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古森同學是自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,內心已經沒有了悲痛  可憐之類的想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只覺得又能少一個人吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金田學姐吃了傷口上的蛆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她已經完全變得不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了逃避恐懼和飢餓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們產生了難以置信的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有誰能代替自己死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我們就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  你趕快去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是  別客氣趕快去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師抓到了鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉這個  振作起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬  有鹿肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部長和老師抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便亂吃肉會得肝炎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經煮過了  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想活下來之後飽受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想做出背叛一姬的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此下決心放棄了吃那些肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音  快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部長和老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡逃出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,離開這座山  回到家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救援已經不會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠自己逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要挑現在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有時間給你細說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盡量快點收拾好行裝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓其他人察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:05:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能帶魔鬼一起走  明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬  你帶我去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜點跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就讓你看看真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千萬別發出大的聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人  原來是這樣的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再仔細看看周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:06:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:06:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓她們逃了  殺了她們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,束縛他們的人類本性已經沒了  互相殘殺要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…一定是在做夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是別把他們當成人類比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時間你們要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐久間學姐  部長和老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音  這個人已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  你們看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐久間學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經和你說過了  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能帶魔鬼一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人已經回不到人類的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會  這一定不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾  周防天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經還挺喜歡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡的人已經不是人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是動物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像獅子吃斑馬是理所當然的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斑馬不會因此生氣或者哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弱肉強食  這便是世界的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是答應過你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會把你救出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼都不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別躲躲藏藏的  快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金田學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}都是誤會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是變為魔鬼了  還是被魔鬼所騙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管如何  那個人也已經回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好和我說  我會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你  站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了  一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經害怕得動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與其被抓住殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個使命就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說我去做誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡面有我偷藏的食物和鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我把能活著逃出深山的辦法寫在了上面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好的看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別放棄  往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要  要拋棄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  我不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會再見的  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬一個人逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要聽我的話  一定會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要回頭  趕緊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一心想要讓自己獲救  而捨棄了一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:10:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是活活遭受最痛苦的方式而死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了救我這樣膽小的女人而犧牲了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最後看見的一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有哭喊  也沒有用怨恨的眼神看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在微笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿在笑著說  這就是命運  這就是法則
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒我  一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:42.14,TXTE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(746,216)}『墜崖第XX天』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後過了多少天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬的背包裡有她偷偷藏起來的點心零食
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我沒有動那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一姬有幸能逃出生天追上我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把這些全都還給她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是現在就屈服吃了這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟那些餓鬼們沒有區別了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有「不能白費這條被一姬救下的命」這個念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,支撐著我在森林裡彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我  一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家肯定是來帶我到天國去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我走不動了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧  我真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣  我犧牲了許許多多的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,獨自一人不知廉恥地活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從事故生還的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被媒體當成奇蹟的生還來報導
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但立刻有人開始懷疑我生還的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只有你活下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:58.95,TXTF,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz277.6\pos(1144,126)}剖析得以生還的\N少女A的陰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:13:59.74,TXTF,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,106)\frz289.6}驗證！\N從現場的碎屍中分析
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:00.45,TXTF,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz244.4\pos(858,156)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}在食物耗盡後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虧你還能裝作沒事一樣生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,換成我肯定不會幹這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要那麼做還不如死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好想活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只有你得救
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你不救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是對活下來的我的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,犧牲他人而活下來的我必須接受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不比死掉的人更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會有人認同我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一個人來懲罰活下來的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要一個人成為我活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那時  最適合給我懲罰的男人出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫風見雄二  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起一直瞞著你  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是犧牲了你的姐姐而活下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知廉恥的卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我第一次見到你的時候就想到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我從雄二身邊奪走了一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那至少讓我代替她陪在你身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二想要我做的事我什麼都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說  你接近我的動機是對我有愧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而並非戀愛感情對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說  雖然我不討厭雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還沒發展到喜歡的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此  我只要能跟雄二在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能給雄二付出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就覺得自己的罪好像減輕了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可我真的  喜歡上了雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我喜歡上雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被你索求就算不上懲罰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我會感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想應該到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算把一切都告訴雄二然後離開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我怎麼道歉一姬都回不來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  你能不能殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有這樣才能受到懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這樣才能得到寬恕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能讓雄二殺了我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  就這樣也喊痛的女人還敢叫我殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你這句話  不要再說對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最討厭這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再說  我的姐姐只有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著你代替一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是讓你不要再說了嗎白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你等等  讓我思考一會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到頭來  你就是喜歡我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  天音  站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我要說的是  我沒打算同情你的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是誰只要活著或多或少都會有後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也明白你的過去不是「後悔」就能形容的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對這樣一輩子都活在痛苦裡後悔的你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼忘掉它或別在意之類的廢話肯定一點用都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才說要我殺了你對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你的命我就收下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你今後一輩子都要為了我而活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是對你的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為我奉獻一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你的國王  你的飼主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以待在雄二身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你敢擅自離開我才不饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊  哭時的臉真難看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好過份  這種時候你就讓人家哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧好吧  不過太吵了我只能批准你哭5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二太不溫柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太溫柔那還能算懲罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能拯救天音的方法只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是接受她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知悉她的過去  接受她的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣她總有一天會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能寬恕自己的  只有自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到她明白的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就待在她身邊  成為她的懲罰好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是全世界都不原諒天音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓我一個人原諒她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話  天音能原諒她自己的那天就肯定會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真覺得一姬死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬的屍體被切碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可找不到頭部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是一個參考數據
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,假如有十個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能偽裝成十一個人的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:19:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一姬她還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我無論如何都想像不到那個一姬會乖乖受死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一姬給我的密林逃脫法小抄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她要我如果逃不出去就回到居留點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上面寫有藏著應急食品的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來一姬從一開始就藏著幾分讓天音逃脫的打算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一姬還活著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得證據一定會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  我們去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回到那現場嗎  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我總有一天要克服的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  我覺得只要跟雄二一起就不會有事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去買供奉用的花和香火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先在這等等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您是風見雄二先生對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  您是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫坂下  是天音的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟她是相當出名的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說她最近交到了男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧  請問您的工作是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到不久前我還是個IT相關企業的董事長來著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是感覺沒了幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊  我想起還有些事沒去做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  突然對您說這種話您也不知該怎麼回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  剛才被一個自稱是你粉絲的奇怪大叔搭話了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不認識  不過感覺很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  射界10厘米
